On Wednesday theNo PERIOD 59UCSB womens tennis team will make a trip to faceNo PERIOD 2USC to start off the  season PERIOD

Santa Barbara wrapped up the previous yearby making a strong run in the postseason making itall the way to the Big West Championship match PERIOD Unfortunately for the Gauchos that is where they fell short to Cal State Long Beach  PERIOD

The Gauchos are hoping to make a return to similar form in order to repeat and improve from last years successes PERIOD Although they lost two seniors this young team have found a new arsenal at their disposal PERIOD

UCSB has two emerging standouts in sophomore Paulina Dubavets and junior Stefani Stojic PERIOD The two have really come together as a powerful duo winning a doubles title at the Jack Kramer Invitational PERIOD Their efforts have been reflectedin their earning aNo PERIOD 21ranking in the doubles category PERIOD

USC has a powerhouse of its own in theduo ofsenior Giuliana Olmos and sophomore Gabby Smith currently ranked No PERIOD  in the nation in doubles PERIOD The Gauchos will have to start the season strong in order to get past a highly Ranked USC Side PERIOD

The match begins Wednesday January twentieth at  p.m PERIOD PST PERIOD at USC PERIOD
